{
  "stem": "8359.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she lived like in the city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I would go to her, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were able to walk, because it wasn't that far.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I would go to her, visit with her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Friends of mine, you know, we try to stay together and--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not at this point.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have to understand that I was taken away so early, that I really don't have the answers to all these questions, because all this came later on.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, it's like, how long can we take this?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I've hadn't-- when they took me away, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] there was no ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, we all lived in our own apartments.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, they were looking for people to work, because, you see, this is my-- how I figured this-- Hitler attacked Russia in 1941, June '41.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Hitler needed man power, because he drafted every able-bodied man.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He drafted.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was too old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Too old.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the same thing in the steeple, and hoping that they don't fall in on you, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like everything else was done, you--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It wasn't permitted.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was forbidden, but they-- and if you couldn't do it, he did it, he prayed in the house.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He'd [INAUDIBLE] in the house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They'd be shot.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I myself did not witness any shootings.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not then.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not then.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sometimes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had like a raid, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They would ride down the street, and pick up a boys, girls.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But what they did with them, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some did, some didn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was taken November 3, 1941.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was asleep, seven o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I heard knocking on the door.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Open up the door, there were two SS men.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They said-- they asked me my name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Get dressed and come.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
